<br />\n不過補完淨低啲粉你擺邊？"},{"pid":"19fd5431ebced0ed87d6c6a21bd9839632872a72","tid":2114132,"uid":6984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"用多樂士 五合一批牆灰"},{"pid":"3be4a2bf89fe95866f1c34620e585cba27d0c314","tid":2114132,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:42:48.000Z","msg":"咪剷左d灰去   買桶即用灰批翻平佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b719beed9e1feb53f06032c216bae29d58c28faa","tid":2114132,"uid":68347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T17:00:15.000Z","msg":"前排屋企裝修,自學剷牆批灰,網上都有好多youtube 教學,希望幫到你<br />\n<br />\n1. 將幅牆甩灰既部份剷走<br />\n<br />\n2. 剷完之後油一層&quot;水性封牆底漆&quot;(施拿),拿返實鬆散既組織<br />\n<br />\n3. 乾左之後用&quot;批牆灰&quot; (立邦有現成一桶賣), 批落你剷走既範圍度<br />\n<br />\n4. 乾左可以上普通底漆<br />\n<br />\n5. 乾左上乳膠漆, 油兩層/三層, 完<br />\n<br />\n(立邦有得買晒你所有要用既野)<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正"},{"pid":"ccd81a60e19e3d22acd6c0f1f0b4aa91714dfb51","tid":2114132,"uid":363108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c3e475c622d549c935b78c5b9bacf66de8ef284","tid":2114132,"uid":249468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:42:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的，屋企d牆甩灰如圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4Gmcvh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4Gmcvh.png&h=3344bc5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2hP5Qn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2hP5Qn.png&h=8d70a75b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想剷掉重練<br />\n但係完全冇裝修經驗，<br />\n唔知剷完之後點補、用咩補<br />\n搵過網上講緊呢幾種：白英泥Vs牆之寶Vs包仔料Vs補牆膏，大概知道有咩分別但係冇人講到究竟用邊隻補小爛嘅牆最好<br />\n另外會拆入牆櫃，但唔知拆完幅牆會爛成點<br />\n想知有咩手尾跟，會嚴重成點？<br />\n有冇人拆過/補過可以講下經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T02:50:41.000Z","msg":"第一張圖唔係咁簡單<br />\n佢個裂痕係由底爆出黎<br />\n如果呢條係樑又好 牆身轉角位又好<br />\n有機會<br />\n1.由底爆出黎-鋼筋生銹（垂直）<br />\n2.批盪唔痴（多年時間冷縮熱漲）<br />\n3.漏水（機會唔大）<br />\n或者其他原因啦<br />\n都建議用炮仔打到無裂痕個層<br />\n而且打既範圍大少少好d 唔好預咁細<br />\n完成上面步驟 可以開始修復<br />\n1.用英泥寶（俗稱牛奶水）溝少少水/唔溝 油一層（油埋格口位）<br />\n2.用膠砂/英泥+沙做批蕩（包埋角）<br />\n3.乾兩日以上再批平膩子（適用埋其他無裂既，因為望落全部都要鏟底）<br />\n4.再用油油兩層（呢層無咁熟，要問油漆師傅）<br />\n利申：泥水仔"},{"pid":"2bc02c6c85923e567564d677dae925d12a0b622f","tid":2114132,"uid":249468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5832fca77b6bb53f77897c17a50b1c17a3b97eca","tid":2114132,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74063cc45b355607dcf274f256e720ff4b77aab5","tid":2114132,"uid":249468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"976f57aced244dd42ef1b48d1e8d07e7f21ca208","tid":2114132,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:50:37.000Z","msg":"鬆嘅剷出嚟先<br />\n買啲ready mix補上去咪得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T15:32:40.000Z","msg":"Ready mix 有冇話咩牌子好？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:39:41.000Z","msg":"唔覺得有分別<br />\n與其聽啲師傅世界大戰不如快快手整咗佢<br />\n你有信心你咪買粉自己溝<br />\n不過補完淨低啲粉你擺邊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:17:13.000Z","msg":"就係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾房應該唔犯法掛"},{"pid":"83e3429ccbfc7100a6abd434ad4d387e107b5b47","tid":2114132,"uid":249468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19fd5431ebced0ed87d6c6a21bd9839632872a72","tid":2114132,"uid":6984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"用多樂士 五合一批牆灰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:18:07.000Z","msg":"打手定真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d1ecf3b0a8b5ed9c474e5046a6d9929aafd54c","tid":2114132,"uid":249468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b719beed9e1feb53f06032c216bae29d58c28fa